A normal young person can have a profile on numerous collective pages, from Facebook to Xanga, and can even merge them with other services, such as Twitter or the last.fm that offers a list of their music habits, then these can be included in a tracking system such as the FriendFeed or the Blip.fm, you can also have a blog, in which the most recent photos are automatically stored in F photos.
